summary: This document is a court filing email transmitting courtesy copies of joint proposed juror questionnaire and voir dire materials in the case US v. Maxwell (20 Cr. 330). It indicates ongoing pre-trial preparations for Ghislaine Maxwell's trial.

events.title: Filing of Joint Proposed Juror Questionnaire and Voir Dire
events.description: The prosecution and defense jointly filed proposed juror questionnaire and voir dire materials with the court in the case US v. Maxwell.

keyFacts: The document is a transmittal email for court filings in the case US v. Maxwell, 20 Cr. 330.
The filings are joint proposed juror questionnaire and voir dire materials, indicating pre-trial jury selection preparations.
The email date is October 13, 2021, showing the timeline of pre-trial procedures in Ghislaine Maxwell's criminal case.
